
Command to enable debug logging

curl -v -X POST http://Administrator:password@127.0.0.1:8091/diag/eval -d 'rpc:eval_everywhere(erlang, apply, [fun () -> [ale:set_loglevel(L, debug) || L <- [couchdb]] end, []]).'


Doc on logging,name and port changes

https://docs.google.com/document/d/1btkHdtK7o2efa8w_p7GZz9GJOULneTWSu_pqI91OzMM/edit?pli=1#heading=h.jczvnhkb9oz1

Config variables for size are: error_logger_mf_max(bytes,files}
